                quantity_per_set, quantity_of_set, unit_id, weight, weight_unit_id,
                note, order_in_day

            SELECT * FROM UNNEST(
                $1::UUID[],
                $2::UUID[],
                $3::UUID[],
                $4::INT[],
                $5::TIMESTAMPTZ[],
                $6::DOUBLE PRECISION[],
                $7::INT[],
                $8::UUID[],
                $9::FLOAT8[],
                $10::UUID[],
                $11::TEXT[],
                $12::INT[]
            )
